{"about_the_game":"HARD VOID is a 4X turn-based strategy game, in a space setting inspired by Lovecraft mythos.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Design your ships! </h2>Highly customizable spaceship designs allow the selection of multiple ship systems: laser cannons, nuclear missiles, fusion reactors and much more :<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/lasercannon_.gif?t=1738997114\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/ftest.gif?t=1738997114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Each spaceship is unique and procedurally generated by your requirements.</h2>The procedural spaceship generator can produce up to 18 Trillion unique spaceships hulls! <br>No two spaceship designs will look the same.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/shipgen.gif?t=1738997114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Conquer the galaxy!</h2>Turn based strategic combat, command hundred of spaceships to battle.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/missiling.gif?t=1738997114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Colonize the galaxy and multiple dimensions!</h2>Use multiple FTL travel methods to explore expand : Warp, Sub, Wormholes and more.<br>Colonize planets, asteroids and the space itself, also you can explore multiple dimensions, but beware,  <br>you aren't only dealing with just other species, space travel unlocks horrors beyond comprehension that are waiting in the vast dark void and will trial your empire.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/galaxy_take2.gif?t=1738997114\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2978460/extras/warping.gif?t=1738997114\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstat